org.springframework.boot.micrometer.metrics.autoconfigure.export.influx.InfluxProperties
@ConfigurationProperties("management.influx.metrics.export") public class InfluxProperties extends StepRegistryProperties
@ConfigurationProperties for configuring Influx metrics export.
